SHG Installation
****************

Prerequisites
-------------

Development environment is Linux debian 2.6.32-5-686 (Debian Squeeze).
Additionaly, GCC 4.8.3 or Clang 3.4.2 and doxygen 1.8.7 are required
for compilation and generating documentation. To compile some
inessential auxiliary programs, Intel Math Kernel Library 11.1.2, GNU
Multiple Precision Arithmetic Library 6.0.0a and Numerical Recipes
Third Edition (version 3.02) are required.

Compilation and testing
-----------------------

Change directory to the main directory of the project. To build the
library, say make lib. To compile the testing program, say make
testing. To run the tests, say make check.

Documentation
-------------

To generate documentation, say make doc. The HTML documentation is
generated in doc/html directory.

Installation
------------

To install the library in /usr/local, say make install. To change the
installation directory, change the prefix variable near the top of
Makefile.
